import React from 'react';
import { Container, Image, Menu } from 'semantic-ui-react';

export default() => (
  <Menu>
    <Container>
      <Menu.Item as='a' header>
        <Image
          size='small'
          icon='ethereum'
        />
      </Menu.Item>

      <Menu.Menu position='right'>
        <Menu.Item as='a' name='login'>
          Login
        </Menu.Item>

        <Menu.Item as='a' name='regiseter'>
          Register
        </Menu.Item>
      </Menu.Menu>
    </Container>
  </Menu>
);
